### [ JOURNALCTL ] Remove logfiles older than 90 days & make sure that, net, the logfiles don't add up to over 5 GB (otherwise trim them back until they do)
# 0 2 * * * root journalctl --vacuum-time=90d --vacuum-size=5G;
